result.name: Tai Hing Roast Restaurant

reviews.text: I love roast goose! Every time i’m back in Hong Kong, I have to eat the roast goose from Tai Hing. However the roast goose I ordered this time was a huge disappointment! It tasted like smoked goose. The skins were burned and tough to chew. This one star is also given to their poor customer service (the to-go area).

Waitresses sometimes got worked up and make noises, but it's understandable because no one can think straight in a workplace busy as hell... overall the meal and the temperature was nicely controlled. I like the motto that says ' nothing beats the real thing'...
Price is above average. Food quality ok
Very hot.  Part of air con down.  Staff open backdoor and there were smell
Stable food quality, branches everywhere for Chinese food but coffee and tea also

result.name: 太興燒味餐廳

reviews.text: 晚市小菜味道錯
太興外賣茶香鷄: 外賣特價68元抵食，經香料煙燻烹調而成，有濃郁的咸香咮。直得一試。但那生鷄的質素不及水準，肉質一般。而且因人多購買，那店一般是預早切好。所以雞的水份蒸發了，而且冷卻。帶回家後用多士爐，輕輕加熱會改善其口感。
以客人心態,你收價錢比其他同業高,但水準退步比以前退步多
現在的太興、舆以前的柤比較、已大大不如、以這價格、吃到這味道、到處都可吃到、而比太興好。

reviews.text: One of the oldest residential site right at the centre of Tai Po. You can have free shuttle buses to the Tai Po Train station. It is also a 5 mins walk to the Tai Po terminus where you can find buses to other urban areas in Hong Kong Island and Kowloon. There are also many good restaurants nearby.
